sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant Gateway as RHOAI Gateway<br/>(Envoy)<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant KRBAC as kube-rbac-proxy<br/>(Sidecar)<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS
    participant API as vLLM OpenAI API<br/>(FastAPI)<br/>8000/TCP HTTP
    participant Engine as AsyncLLM Engine<br/>(v1 Engine)
    participant HFHub as Hugging Face Hub<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant S3 as S3 Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    Note over Client,S3: Flow 1: Inference Request (OpenAI-compatible)

    Client->>Gateway: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (OAuth/OIDC)<br/>TLS 1.2+
    Gateway->>KRBAC: Forward request<br/>HTTPS/8443<br/>Service Account Token
    KRBAC->>API: Forward (authed)<br/>HTTP/8000 plaintext (localhost)<br/>Bearer Token (API key, optional)

    Note over API,Engine: AuthenticationMiddleware validates<br/>SHA-256 hash of bearer token

    API->>Engine: Inference request<br/>(in-process or ZeroMQ IPC)
    Engine->>Engine: PagedAttention +<br/>Continuous Batching

    alt Streaming Response (SSE)
        Engine-->>API: Token chunks (async generator)
        API-->>KRBAC: SSE stream chunks
        KRBAC-->>Gateway: SSE stream
        Gateway-->>Client: text/event-stream<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS 1.2+
    else Non-Streaming Response
        Engine-->>API: Complete response
        API-->>KRBAC: JSON response
        KRBAC-->>Gateway: Forward response
        Gateway-->>Client: application/json<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS 1.2+
    end

    Note over Client,S3: Flow 2: Model Loading (Startup)

    Engine->>HFHub: GET model weights/tokenizer/config<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (HF_TOKEN)
    HFHub-->>Engine: Model artifacts (safetensors/bin)

    alt Alternative: S3 Storage
        Engine->>S3: GET model artifacts<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: AWS IAM (S3_ACCESS_KEY_ID/SECRET)
        S3-->>Engine: Model artifacts
    end

    Engine->>Engine: Load weights to memory<br/>(CPU, quantized INT4/INT8/FP8)
